

Refer 

https://huongdanjava.com/fix-error-fatal-error-compiling-tools-jar-not-found-of-apache-maven-on-eclipse.html

window-> preferences --> java --> Installed JRE's 

then select target jre and edit the path

box will be prompted which holds the JRE home & JRE name (fill the path exact values)

click on add external jar --> select tools.jar from jdk/lib/tools.jar

and complete the apply 



                     :):) done with resolving
